OL,3,CSenedd 2026 is 'a choice between Plaid
OL,4,Cand Reform' - leader to tell conference
OL,6,FThis year's Senedd Election is 'a
OL,7,Fstraight choice between Plaid and
OL,8,FReform', Rhun ap Iorwerth will tell
OL,9,Fhis party's conference today.
OL,11,FSpeaking to delegates in Newport,
OL,12,FPlaid Cymru's leader will tell party
OL,13,Fmembers that the election is a choice
OL,14,Fbetween "tolerance or division" and
OL,15,F"progress or decay", adding that "the
OL,16,Fparty is over for Labour".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
