OL,3,CSenedd 2026 is 'a choice between Plaid
OL,4,Cand Reform' - leader to tell conference
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru saw an increase in its
OL,7,Fvote share to 37% in ITV Cymru Wales'
OL,8,Flatest YouGov poll in January this
OL,9,Fyear - up from 30% in September, with
OL,10,FReform UK dropping from 29% to 23%.
OL,12,FRhun ap Iorwerth will today accuse
OL,13,FReform UK of using Wales as an
OL,14,F"electoral springboard", whilst having
OL,15,F"no accountability, no seriousness and
OL,16,Fno policies."
OL,18,FHe will tell party delegates: "We
OL,19,Foffer hope - hope that can overcome
OL,20,Fpeople's fears of other political
OL,21,Fforces leading Wales down a dark path.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@_OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
