CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772223642
OL,3,CSenedd 2026 is 'a choice between Plaid
OL,4,Cand Reform' - leader to tell conference
OL,6,F"Hope that things can get better for
OL,7,Four Health Service, that our elderly
OL,8,Frelatives won't have to wait so long
OL,9,Ffor treatment or that the burden of
OL,10,Fchildcare costs on our sons and
OL,11,Fdaughters' household budgets will be
OL,12,Feased.
OL,14,F"And hope that, finally, Wales will
OL,15,Fhave a government willing to stand up
OL,16,Fto Keir Starmer, to Jo Stevens and
OL,17,Fanyone else denying our nation the
OL,18,Ffairness it deserves."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@VO]
