OL,3,CSenedd 2026 is 'a choice between Plaid
OL,4,Cand Reform' - leader to tell conference
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV Wales, sent direct
OL,9,Fto your inbox every Saturday morning.
OL,11,FDan Thomas, Leader of Reform Wales,
OL,12,Fhas responded to the Plaid leader's
OL,13,Fplanned speech.
OL,15,FHe said: "In May, Wales has a clear
OL,16,Fchoice in the election. On the one
OL,17,Fhand is Plaid, who have propped Labour
OL,18,Fup for a generation, supporting
OL,19,Fpolicies like the Nation of Sanctuary
OL,20,Fand blanket 20mph speed limits.
OL,26,@wD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
