PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772223642
OL,3,CSenedd 2026 is 'a choice between Plaid
OL,4,Cand Reform' - leader to tell conference
OL,6,F"On the other is Reform, who are the
OL,7,Fonly party that can deliver the real
OL,8,Fchange Wales deserves."
OL,10,FPlaid Cymru will soon launch its
OL,11,F'First 100 Days' plan for government,
OL,12,Fwith Rhun ap Iorwerth MS expected to
OL,13,Fsay he wants to "do politics
OL,14,Fdifferently in Wales".
OL,16,FHe'll say: "We aim to be known as a
OL,17,Fteam that runs a better government, or
OL,18,Fquite simply got the basics right.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@WO]
