OL,3,CSenedd 2026 is 'a choice between Plaid
OL,4,Cand Reform' - leader to tell conference
OL,6,F"We'll be people centred, thinking
OL,7,Falways of the impact our policies,
OL,8,Flegislation and actions will have on
OL,9,Fpeople's lives in Wales. We'll be
OL,10,Fopen, transparent and digitally
OL,11,Fdriven, sharing information and
OL,12,Finsights, highlighting opportunities
OL,13,Fand challenges ` to build a new
OL,14,Fconfidence and a new trust in our
OL,15,FWelsh democracy."
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
